stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> queued : POST creates job
    queued --> running : worker picks up (one at a time)
    running --> running : stage advances (progress %)
    running --> awaiting_user : approval gate / Colab import
    awaiting_user --> running : user approves / uploads render
    running --> done : all stages complete
    running --> failed : exception (stderr tail captured)
    queued --> cancelled : user cancel
    running --> cancelled : user cancel (between stages)
    failed --> queued : user retry
    done --> [*]
